{"tid":1350790,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)罪惡城 私刑教育 烈探狙擊","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T20:30:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a34de9d3c352938156e67d88676a412b2ad50b","tid":1350790,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=777e5316\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=e1411e8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8c7a0512\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d1/Jack_Reacher_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd1%2FJack_Reacher_poster.jpg&h=effc1eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/24/Sincityposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F24%2FSincityposter.jpg&h=afcb361d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Equalize_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Equalize_poster.jpg&h=24b407cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.講述三個故事：Sin City，The Big Fat Kill和That Yellow Bastard。這三個故事都發生在一個虛構的城市&mdash;罪惡之城，而在這座城市中，主教大人、參議員、警察卻正是罪惡的根源。故事由米基&middot;洛克所扮演的醜陋的大塊頭Marv開始。他與漂亮女人歌迪發生了一夜情，歌迪的美貌與柔情令他有一種被救贖的感覺，並讓他第一次感受到來自女人的&ldquo;愛&rdquo;。但當MARV半夜驚醒，卻發現睡在身邊的歌迪已經被殺。他卻成警方追捕的對象。 MARY為抓住殺死歌迪的真兇，展開了復仇之旅<br />\n<br />\n2.一名為曾為政府工作的前中情局成員化名為羅柏&middot;麥考現住在麻薩諸塞州的波士頓，並在一間五金賣場上班。他協助他的同事朋友拉爾夫減重，以便通過保安考試。麥考答應已過世的妻子，絕不會再回到過去的危險生活。因妻子生前很愛看書，麥考為了達到讀滿100本書，下班後他習慣帶著一包茶包到住家附近一間餐廳看書，日復一日，過著平靜的生活..<br />\n<br />\n3.一個尋常的小鎮，一如往常的早晨，五個人照常過日子，卻慘遭隨機射殺。所有證據都指向一個人：槍法神準的殺手，他前身是軍人，訓練有素的狙擊兵。他很快就遭到逮捕與拘提。經過漫長的訊問，依然問不出什麼。囚犯只做出一個神祕的要求，隨手寫下：「給我Jack Reacher」。誰是Jack？這問題令人費解..<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=92af1e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=249664a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6adceb4911aa50fdcd